205
00:13:18,314 --> 00:13:19,815
Sebaiknya begitu!

206
00:13:19,815 --> 00:13:21,317
Begitu.

207
00:13:21,317 --> 00:13:24,420
Kurasa dia begitu gugup dengan hal lainnya.

208
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:25,721
Benar-benar.

209
00:13:25,721 --> 00:13:30,426
