214
00:13:44,807 --> 00:13:48,811
Dia berusaha sangat keras untuk melayaniku.

215
00:13:50,613 --> 00:13:54,216
Maksudku, sampai hidupnya habis.

216
00:13:59,021 --> 00:14:02,324
